'From Squeak3.6beta of ''4 July 2003'' [latest update: #5402] on 6 October 2003 at 11:35:58 am'!"Change Set:		fcb-noMessages-asmDate:			2 October 2003Author:			Alejandro Magistrelloopen a file-contents-browser, (a) Make sure no class is selected.(b) Click on the ""Class"" button.(c) Click in the (empty) selector-list pane.i modified FileContentsBrowser.selectedClassOrMetaClass to simulate the one in Browser."!!FileContentsBrowser methodsFor: 'metaclass' stamp: 'asm 10/6/2003 11:29'!selectedClassOrMetaClass	"Answer the selected class or metaclass."	| cls |	self metaClassIndicated		ifTrue: [^ (cls _ self selectedClass) ifNotNil: [cls metaClass]]		ifFalse: [^ self selectedClass]! !